sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Backend as ODH Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: User Authentication and Dashboard Access

    User->>Router: GET /<br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>OAuth: OAuth Challenge<br/>HTTPS/443
    OAuth->>User: OAuth Token (cookie)<br/>HTTPS/443
    User->>Proxy: GET / + Bearer Token<br/>HTTPS/8443
    Proxy->>Backend: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>X-Auth-Request-User header
    Backend->>K8sAPI: List CRs<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: CR data
    Backend-->>Proxy: Dashboard HTML/JS
    Proxy-->>User: Dashboard UI

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Notebook Creation

    User->>Proxy: POST /api/notebooks<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token
    Proxy->>Backend: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>X-Auth-Request-User
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook created
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create PVC<br/>HTTPS/6443
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: PVC created
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create RoleBinding<br/>HTTPS/6443
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: RoleBinding created
    Backend-->>Proxy: Success response
    Proxy-->>User: JSON response

    Note over User,Prom: Flow 3: Metrics Query (Prometheus)

    User->>Proxy: GET /api/prometheus<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token
    Proxy->>Backend: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>X-Auth-Request-User
    Backend->>Prom: Query metrics<br/>HTTP/9091<br/>Bearer Token
    Prom-->>Backend: Metrics data
    Backend-->>Proxy: Metrics response
    Proxy-->>User: JSON metrics
